          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Energy distributions of photoneutrons from nuclei",
                "Rh-103, Ta-181, Au-197 and Bi-209 at the",
                "bremsstrahlung end-point energy En-max=28.5 MeV have",
                "been measured for the sum of neutrons outgoing for the",
                "angles from ang-min to ang-max in nuclear emulsions.",
                "The obtained photoneutron energy distributions",
                "and the quantum measured by the authors earlier",
                "for the same nuclei, but at different value of",
                "en-max, are compared with calculations within the",
                "evaporation model and the hybrid model of",
                "pre-equilibrium decay."
              ]
            }
          ],
